title: Marvel chronology disk 19 v2.0 (dimlan)
description:
People frequently ask me for a "reading order" list. I don&#039;t have one. I use an Excel worksheet to compile a chronological order and then use it over again, so I don&#039;t have anything saved. 

I did begin to put together a list when I started reposting the disks on the pirate bay. So far I have disks 1-18, 21-31 and 74-82. Anyone interested can find them the thread in the "comic book discussions" section at ZCult, if you&#039;re a member.
